# End-of-pass GitHub + Netlify (KCCC)

After any interaction that modifies tracked files in `Kelly-calendar`:

1. Commit and `git push` to origin (never stage `.env.local` or secrets).
2. Deploy production: stop local `next dev` if running, then `npm run deploy:netlify:prod`.
3. Report branch, commit hash, push status, and Netlify deploy result.

Authoritative notes: `develop_notes/KCCC_END_OF_PASS_GITHUB_AND_NETLIFY.md`.
